# § I> CSL3-glyph-native ≤ 250 LOC · POD-1-A3
# § I> consumed-by POD-2-B2 cssl-host-roguelike-run crate
# § I> ⊑ specs/31_LOA_DESIGN.csl + GDDs/LOA_PILLARS.md
