            CHARACTER-progression (cross-run) vs RUN-progression (in-run) ?
  Q-RL-2 : asynchronous-versus-mode (race-against-friend's-ghost-replay) :
            in-or-out for v1 ? gift-economy-axiom suggests OUT but ⊘
  Q-RL-3 : Endless-Spire run-cap (∞ vs soft-cap @ floor-50) ?
  Q-RL-4 : Companion-class-affinity : does-Companion-prefer-some-classes ?
  Q-RL-5 : seasonal-hard-perma cadence (monthly · quarterly · player-driven) ?

